<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><alert xmlns="urn:oasis:names:tc:emergency:cap:1.2"><identifier>2.49.0.0.554.0.tswarning.ch.20251226233752552.0</identifier><sender>https://www.metservice.com</sender><sent>2025-12-27T12:37:52+13:00</sent><status>Actual</status><msgType>Alert</msgType><scope>Public</scope><info><category>Met</category><event>Thunderstorm</event><responseType>Prepare</responseType><urgency>Immediate</urgency><severity>Severe</severity><certainty>Observed</certainty><onset>2025-12-27T12:30:00+13:00</onset><expires>2025-12-27T13:30:00+13:00</expires><senderName>Meteorological Service of New Zealand Limited</senderName><headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning</headline><description>At 12:30 pm, MetService weather radar detected severe thunderstorms near THE HUNTERS HILLS.

These severe thunderstorms are moving towards the eastnortheast, and are expected to lie near THE HUNTERS HILLS at 01:00 pm and near THE HUNTERS HILLS at 01:30 pm.

These thunderstorms are expected to be accompanied by large hail.

Impact:

Large hail can cause significant damage to crops, orchards, vines, glasshouses and vehicles, and make driving conditions hazardous.</description><instruction>The National Emergency Management Agency advises that as storms approach you should:
    - Take shelter, preferably indoors away from windows;
    - Avoid sheltering under trees, if outside;
    - Get back to land, if outdoors on the water;
    - Move cars under cover or away from trees;
    - Secure any loose objects around your property;
    - Check that drains and gutters are clear;
    - Be ready to slow down or stop, if driving.
During and after the storm, you should also:
    - Beware of fallen trees and power lines;
    - Avoid streams and drains as you may be swept away in flash flooding.</instruction><web>https://www.metservice.com/warnings/home</web><parameter><valueName>ColourCode</valueName><value>Red</value></parameter><parameter><valueName>ColourCodeHex</valueName><value>#FF181E</value></parameter><area><areaDesc>Timaru,Waimate</areaDesc><polygon>-44.467,170.890 -44.505,170.909 -44.529,170.929 -44.542,170.949 -44.548,170.974 -44.550,171.001 -44.549,171.038 -44.538,171.092 -44.532,171.111 -44.523,171.127 -44.507,171.139 -44.483,171.149 -44.461,171.146 -44.426,171.141 -44.407,171.133 -44.384,171.117 -44.372,171.099 -44.365,171.074 -44.361,171.045 -44.366,171.000 -44.379,170.946 -44.393,170.921 -44.412,170.899 -44.442,170.889 -44.467,170.890</polygon></area></info><Signature xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/09/xmldsig#"><SignedInfo><CanonicalizationMethod Algorithm="http://www.w3.org/TR/2001/REC-xml-c14n-20010315#WithComments"/><SignatureMethod Algorithm="http://www.w3.org/2001/04/xmldsig-more#rsa-sha256"/><Reference URI=""><Transforms><Transform Algorithm="http://www.w3.org/2000/09/xmldsig#enveloped-signature"/></Transforms><DigestMethod Algorithm="http://www.w3.org/2001/04/xmlenc#sha256"/><DigestValue>EzEH9v+A37bq39oUUQQhq5M5myjVa9YmyNUwQyFrhs8=</DigestValue></Reference></SignedInfo><SignatureValue>yJsEH5BnjEW2vEqM/JcfJxj+YBGOOaQrNT12NVCjwrxbHM5VDwY2ecriIsT3j4fEihdJaydY+M6/&#13;
